(43, 8, 1, 40, 21, 1, 1, 'mount of Olives', 'Connection through Mount of Olives', 'Both passages emphasize the mount of Olives as a significant location in Jesus'' ministry. This connection highlights the geographical continuity in the narrative of Jesus'' journey.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
