(43, 8, 11, 23, 1, 16, 18, 'go, and sin no more', 'Forgiveness and Cleansing from Sin', 'This connection highlights the theme of forgiveness and the call to cease sinning. Both passages emphasize the importance of making oneself clean and turning away from evil actions.', 'theme', 0.496, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 8, 11, 42, 15, 7, 7, 'Neither do I condemn thee', 'Repentance and Forgiveness Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of forgiveness and the joy of repentance. In both passages, Jesus emphasizes the importance of not condemning sinners and the joy in heaven when one repents.', 'theme', 0.43299999999999994, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 8, 11, 42, 5, 32, 32, 'go, and sin no more', 'Jesus'' Call to Repentance', 'This connection highlights Jesus'' mission to offer forgiveness and encourage repentance. Both passages emphasize His compassion towards sinners and the call to change one''s life.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 8, 11, 18, 34, 31, 31, 'go, and sin no more', 'Forgiveness and Transformation', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of repentance and the call to avoid sin after receiving forgiveness. In John, Jesus instructs the woman to ''go, and sin no more,'' while in Job, the speaker expresses a commitment to not offend God again after chastisement.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 8, 11, 20, 28, 13, 13, 'neither do I condemn thee', 'Mercy and Forgiveness Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of acknowledging sin and the mercy that follows. John 8:11 highlights Jesus'' forgiveness, while Proverbs 28:13 underscores the necessity of confessing and forsaking sin to receive mercy.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 8, 12, 43, 9, 5, 5, 'I am the light of the world', 'Light of the World Connection', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus as ''the light of the world.'' This connection highlights the continuity of Jesus'' identity and mission in bringing illumination to those who follow him.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
