(43, 8, 42, 43, 12, 49, 49, 'neither came I of myself, but he sent me', 'Connection of Divine Sending', 'Both passages emphasize that Jesus was sent by the Father and did not act on his own authority. This connection highlights the relationship between Jesus and God as one of divine mission and obedience.', 'theme', 0.986, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
